  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Italy Ski Holidays by Rail 2023 / 2024</h2>
<p>Experience Italy's enchanting winter landscapes like never before as you journey by rail.</p>
<div class="c-tabs-beta__content-table--row-wrapper">
<p><img src="/media/13062743/italy_the-dolomites-ski-area_skiers-action-mountains2.jpg" alt="italyresorts" data-udi="umb://media/b5a1f05ab5824df69ffa001e3009da49" /></p>
<h3>Travel by Rail to Italy</h3>
<p>If you are seeking fresh piste and blue-bird mornings this ski season, then hop on the train and visit <a data-udi="umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902" href="/{localLink:umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902}" title="Italy">Italy</a> as part of an Inghams ski or snowboard holiday. </p>
<p>Thoughts of fresh snow are always at the forefront of any avid skier and therefore any Inghams ski holiday. Join us in future proofing our snow falls and travel by train instead of plane. </p>
<p>Searching for that first snowfall? Book online by selecting St Pancras for departure or <a data-udi="umb://document/e5b8abf94a554299a3960566b88e9193" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e5b8abf94a554299a3960566b88e9193}" title="Contact Us">contact us</a> to find out more. </p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></p>
